1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,950
♪Obsessions penned
into an everlasting love♪

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Affections gently linger
around fingertips♪

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:23,140
♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 11]

13
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:06,500
It's the night of the full moon again.

14
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:08,940
I have been here for a month.

15
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,020
What are you thinking?

16
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:21,420
Master.

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:25,460
You are quite reticent, huh?

18
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,580
The fifteenth of every month

19
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:29,220
is the day you take
the Soul-shattering Pill.

20
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:31,300
If I didn't come today,

21
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:33,100
how would you manage the pain?

22
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:38,300
Come and eat with me.

23
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:39,980
Let me do it.

24
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:58,340
Thank you...

25
00:01:58,340 --> 00:02:00,260
Do away with formalities tonight.

26
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:06,860
I remember

27
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,580
your sister is

28
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,220
six years younger than you.

29
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:14,500
Back then,

30
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:17,180
I entrusted her to a merchant in Yuzhou.

31
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:18,820
In the past ten years,

32
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,940
have you visited her?

33
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,340
No.

34
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:23,940
Don't you miss her?

35
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,220
You made a good arrangement for her.

36
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:28,780
There is no need for me to worry.

37
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:38,620
Why did you bring this up
all of a sudden?

38
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,940
Do you know the man

39
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,380
who came to me at the pavilion
earlier today?

40
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,100
It's Second Young Master.

41
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:53,700
We used to be tight
when we were young.

42
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,980
However, the time we were close

43
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:58,100
was

44
00:02:58,660 --> 00:03:00,180
when I didn't know
he was my biological brother.

45
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:06,580
Try this.

46
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,580
The pear-flavored tea pastry.

47
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:10,180
My favorite when I was a kid.

48
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:30,700
Master.

49
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,700
Do you know about the Juntian Token?

50
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:36,780
All I know is

51
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,540
that only the leader of the Shadow Sect
possesses this token

52
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,420
to give commands.

53
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,580
You may not know about this.

54
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:45,020
Before Ling Yuanzheng became the leader,

55
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,980
Shadow Sect adopts the slaughter system.

56
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,260
Those capable

57
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:50,500
could challenge the leader
of the Shadow Sect.

58
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:51,900
If they win,

59
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,700
they could replace the master.

60
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:57,820
Are you suggesting...

61
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:00,180
Master Ling's birthday banquet
is around the corner.

62
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,540
If what you said is true,

63
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,100
the Shadow Sect

64
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:07,220
would be the major variable.

65
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,620
I could obtain the Juntian Token

66
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:15,620
to ease your burden.

67
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,980
Chiye is highly skilled,

68
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:23,100
and even Ling Yuanzheng is wary of him.

69
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:25,140
If that day...

70
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:26,820
I know this is going
to be very dangerous.

71
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:28,860
But I said

72
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,460
I would keep you safe.

73
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,540
Shadow Sect summons you?

74
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:42,660
Yes.

75
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:49,140
Please trust me.

76
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:52,500
I won't fail you.

77
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:02,780
Over the past decade,

78
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:06,660
I have never trusted anyone.

79
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:08,300
Yingshi.

80
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:10,660
You are the only one.

81
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:13,500
Don't fail me.

82
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,860
If you don't doubt me,

83
00:05:19,940 --> 00:05:20,740
I

84
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,500
will never fail you,
even at the cost of my life.

85
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:49,940
Why didn't you come here

86
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:52,380
when I summoned you that day?

87
00:05:53,380 --> 00:05:55,660
Young Master drugged me and teased me.

88
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,220
I was worried she might doubt me

89
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,740
if I came.

90
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:05,700
I instructed you

91
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:08,580
to find the Wanxin Manual

92
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,140
while Ling Xuan was away.

93
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:11,980
Why did you

94
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:15,380
go to the main hall?

95
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:19,060
Mr. Ya made me

96
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,820
escort Young Master to the main hall.

97
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:22,620
I thought he suspected me.

98
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,860
I dared not act rashly

99
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:27,380
and thought there would be
another opportunity in the future.

100
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:29,100
The priority was to reassure him.

101
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:31,940
Therefore, I had to offend Master Ling

102
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,860
and rescue Ling Xuan from the main hall

103
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,140
so as to win her trust.

104
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:41,580
Does Ling Xuan

105
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,220
trust you now?

106
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:49,140
I have her complete trust by now.

107
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,660
Even so,

108
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,140
you ignored my summon

109
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,180
and defied orders twice.

110
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,620
I must punish you.

111
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,100
Today is a warning.

112
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:20,140
Master Ling's birthday banquet
is in two days.

113
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,540
Young Master

114
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,980
will go to the main hall alone.

115
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,380
Take this opportunity

116
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:27,180
to eliminate the entire Xuantian House.

117
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:31,500
If there is any mistake again,

118
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:33,980
you know the consequences.

119
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:37,980
I will do

120
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,180
as you command.

121
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:47,260
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

122
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:50,860
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

123
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:53,140
♪Goodbye♪

124
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:57,180
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

125
00:07:58,460 --> 00:08:01,790
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

126
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:05,500
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

127
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:08,180
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

128
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,780
♪I only wish your eyes♪

129
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:12,860
♪As pure as snow♪
